{"tha-ap158:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap158:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap158:0.3":"Kadambapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap158:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap158:1.2":"kukkuto nama pabbato; ","tha-ap158:1.3":"Tamhi pabbatapadamhi, ","tha-ap158:1.4":"satta buddha vasanti te. ","tha-ap158:2.1":"Kadambam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap158:2.2":"diparajamva uggatam; ","tha-ap158:2.3":"Ubho hatthehi paggayha, ","tha-ap158:2.4":"satta buddhe samokirim. ","tha-ap158:3.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap158:3.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap158:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap158:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap158:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap158:4.2":"sattasum pupphanamaka; ","tha-ap158:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap158:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap158:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap158:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap158:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap158:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kadambapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap158:7.1":"Kadambapupphiyattherassapadanam chattham. "}